structure.unit: ARTICLE LII. MIAMI-DADE COUNTY ADVISORY COMMITTEE ON GROUND TRANSPORTATION REGULATION

text.section:
Sec. 2-585. Report.
The committee shall submit a written report thereon to the Clerk of the Board of County Commissioners on May 31, 1994 relating to the written recommendations and accompanying ordinance amendments of the county manager prepared in accordance with. Upon submission of its report, the committee shall be dissolved.
